Parliament, Wednesday, 19 June 2019 – Accredited media representatives who will cover the 2019 State of the Nation Address scheduled for tomorrow, 20 June 2019 are urged to collect their accreditation tags at No. 49 Hope Street (Government Garage), Cape Town – this accreditation point is located about 500 meters away from Parliament.
	
	GENERAL INFORMATION Please contact the following media officials for any enquiries: ISSUED BY PARLIAMENT OF THE REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA Enquiries: Moloto Mothapo  – 082 370 6930 Democracy is not an event that occurred in 1994. It is a process to which all of us can contribute by making our voices heard in Parliament, in the provincial legislatures and in broader society.Read more